## Pillar 3: Performance & Core Web Vitals

### Grade: A-

### вњ… Resolved Since v1
- вњ… **Font loading optimized.** Render-blocking `@import` replaced with `next/font/google`. Inter is now self-hosted, eliminating external network round-trip. `--font-inter` CSS variable correctly referenced in `globals.css`.
- вњ… **Mobile GPU blur reduced.** `blur-[80px] md:blur-[150px]` on all three ambient glow orbs in `BackgroundEffects`. ~50% GPU memory reduction on mobile.
- вњ… **Scroll listener throttled.** `requestAnimationFrame` + `{ passive: true }` in `Navbar` prevents per-pixel main-thread blocking.
- вњ… **CLS spinners eliminated.** No more `next/dynamic` loading states causing Cumulative Layout Shift.

